    <p>This is a real day. Every food below is something you can buy at any grocery store, most in under 5 minutes of prep. The running total after each meal shows you where you stand in real time — the same feedback loop the app provides.</p>

    <p><strong>Don't copy this exactly — understand the pattern.</strong> The specific foods are interchangeable. The structure is what matters.</p>

