        <div class="faq-a">Protein contains 4 calories per gram, so 120g contributes roughly 480 calories from protein alone. The total day's calorie count depends on your food sources — a day built around Greek yogurt, cottage cheese, and lean chicken will run significantly lower in total calories than one centered on red meat.</div>
